{"tid":1434045,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【殺人武器討論】認識香港抗爭常見的致命武器（純學術）","createTime":"2019-08-08T16:03:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T15:41:54.000Z","uid":35699,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"17a8ffc8701de20e3d85eced12002f349bbd6ffe","tid":1434045,"uid":35699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T16:03:27.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">好似無人討論過抗爭現場經常見到既武器</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gzvHCmk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgzvHCmk.png&h=b344398e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">催淚性神經毒氣</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">用熱分散法可造成毒煙，也可用爆炸法或撒粉器造成微粉使地面和空氣染毒。能刺激眼睛、呼吸道和皮膚，有強烈噴嚏和催淚作用。氣溶膠對人眼的刺激閾值為0.0025mg/m3，最低刺激濃度為0.1～1.0mg/m3。皮膚接觸有灼燒感，疼痛感，嚴重時出現水泡、潰瘍。野戰條件下，一般不會造成致死性傷害。氣溶膠狀態的CS對眼睛和上呼吸道具有強烈的刺激作用，中毒後會出現灼痛、大量流淚流鼻涕等症狀，脫離接觸5～15分鐘後症狀就會消失,但皮膚接觸的地方會產生刺痛、紅斑，其作用仍可保持數小時之久。<br />\n<br />\n毒理試驗證明後接觸到CS死亡的動物顯示杯狀細胞數量的增加，呼吸道及結膜（眼睛粘膜，眼瞼和覆蓋眼球的一部分），呼吸道和消化道壞死（細胞死亡），肺水腫（肺部充滿液體），並腎上腺出血。 </span><br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/no2VXmm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fno2VXmm.png&h=62fec3dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">四十毫米口徑榴彈</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">40毫米榴彈是一種軍用榴彈，用於各式各樣的榴彈發射器，在多國軍隊內服役。由於韓戰爆發時，受敵軍人海戰術的影響，損失慘重。故美軍以二戰日軍的榴彈擲彈筒為基準，展開Niblick Project計畫，研發出40毫米榴彈。其具有稱之為高低壓（High Low Pressure）的結構，使其在很低的膛壓下，可以發射出去。</span><br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/48tFo1o.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F48tFo1o.png&h=ceff1977&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">刺激性辣椒水</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">在香港，即使將調味用辣椒醬、辣椒油等放進噴霧瓶中噴灑，模仿類似胡椒噴霧效果，亦會被視作藏有攻擊性武器屬犯法（儘管這些模仿品實際刺激性及所造成傷害遠比真正胡椒噴霧低得多）</span><br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xsPM31q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxsPM31q.png&h=0df873bf&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">Remington M870</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">霰彈（shotgun shell，或shotshell）[1][2]，或稱散彈[3]，是一種裝有霰彈丸（shot）或霰彈塊（slug）的子彈，霰彈專門設計成以霰彈槍來發射。）</span>"},{"pid":"66a843dc14b666a3e58279e9e19a569f7311c328","tid":1434045,"uid":35699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T16:03:40.000Z","msg":"輕推"},{"pid":"e65be108767c1e7b058ef5afcdfcba403203ae0a","tid":1434045,"uid":35699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T16:06:32.000Z","msg":"【殺人武器討論】認識香港抗爭常見的致命武器（純學術）<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1434045\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1434045</a>"},{"pid":"36727212d43aa3aa2378d88711a02257740d2e4a","tid":1434045,"uid":35699,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T16:11:19.000Z","msg":"無人想知"},{"pid":"92b3523677168a1526882615d9f32a948d665e31","tid":1434045,"uid":35699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T16:11:29.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"fe1cbdc0f5c86caf704427f349e77d2fe8265dd9","tid":1434045,"uid":35699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T16:11:39.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"c6d308ed1ae1d54589e6e02120dcc91c244d0690","tid":1434045,"uid":35699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T16:11:49.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"6e6342a9c204331da94d57ac6d155b998c6b6de2","tid":1434045,"uid":35699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T16:11:59.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"3f3d4b8d6733ac5abb570443b6b6e624b988d9fc","tid":1434045,"uid":142007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T16:12:07.000Z","msg":"<